captions.text:
"Improbable Scenes",
everybody plays!

You wrote scene suggestions
and put them in this red box,

I'll get your suggestions
and read them,

then whoever has an idea will
step up and do it, just like that.
For instance:
'What will the iPhone 10 be like'?
Good, it's charged.

What do you mean, it's so
expensive you had to sell a kidney?

Yeah, but you can download
the dialysis app and you're cool!
Awesome!
'New uses for a Rubik's Cube'
Amazing.
Yellow card.

- You should have given the red card!
- I can't solve the red side...
C'mon, referee...
'Improbable endings for El Chavo'
Take this!

- That's child abuse, sir...
- Wait a minute... Come on...

- It's been 14 years...
- Don Ramón got arrested!

- Mommy! Mommy!
- What's up, my precious?

- He hit me!
- I can't believe this...
You crazy? You crazy?
You're hurting my wrist!

Call your husband! Where's your
husband? Don't you have a husband?

Would you like to come inside
and get a cup of coffee?

Forget the coffee,
I wanna fuck!
That's Mr. Sausage...

'Best excuses for
not washing the dishes'

- Can you wash the dishes?
- I can't, I'm... I'm allergic to dishes.
But you ate on the dishes...

- What?
- Now it's your turn to wash the dishes.

I want them all clean
when I get back.
Mom, they're broken!
You'll wash them piece by piece!

- What?
- I won't wash the dishes.

Have you ever asked them
if they want to be washed?

That's racist, man,
that's bullying, you know?

- The dishes can't choose...
- What are you saying, plate?

What? Opression?
That's what I thought!

'What if the Great Wall
of China was brazilian'?

- Wait, where's the wall?
- Relax, it will be ready for the World Cup...

- It should have been ready in 300 BC, dammit!
- 2300 years ain't that long...

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented

IMPROVÁVEL
Probably a good show.
Freeze!

'What are the thoughts
of a curtain'?
